<h4 data-index="4990"><span class="red" data-index="4991">Instructions</span></h4>
<p class="latin1" data-index="4992"><span class="label" data-index="4993"><b data-index="4994">a.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Journalize the annual adjusting entries that were made.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="4995"><span class="label" data-index="4996"><b data-index="4997">b.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Prepare an income statement for the year ending December 31, 2020, and a balance sheet at <span data-index="4998">December 3</span>1.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="4999"><span class="label" data-index="5000"><b data-index="5001">c.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Describe the remaining steps in the accounting cycle to be completed by Nalezny for 2020.</p>
