<p data-index="5421">Compute the amount of depreciation expense (related to the mower and accessories) that should be reported on Boston’s December 31, 2020, income statement. Assume straight-line depreciation.</p>
<p data-index="5422"><b class="codeColorBlue2" data-index="5423">14.</b> Midwest Enterprises made the following entry on December 31, 2020.</p>
